      <span class="headers">Xanthe`s Earring/PoTC - The Sacrifice of Nine</span>
<p>
<p>
<i>After all nine gifts have been made, they must be "sacrificed" to the forge. Original writeup courtesy of Xanthe Ravenwolf</i>
</p>
<p>
Place all of your finely crafted nine gifts (<a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=1650&menustr=">demi-sec champagne</a>, <a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=1621&menustr=">mistletoe cutting sickle</a>, <a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=1469&menustr=">golden idol of tunare</a>, <a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=1758&menustr=">blessed fishing rod</a>, <a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=1470&menustr=">star ruby encrusted stein</a>, <a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=1473&menustr=">ceremonial solstice robe</a>, <a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=1767&menustr=">lotus pie</a>, <a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=1139&menustr=">misty thicket picnic</a>, <a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=1140&menustr=">lucky cabbage</a>) into a <a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=1610&menustr=">forge</a> (any normal, non-cultural forge), and hit combine (fear not, it is a no-fail combine). The faithful (or is that crazed, by this point in your questing?) shall recieve:
</p>
<p>
<b><a href="/items/show_item.php?item=1111&menustr=">xanthe's earring of nature</a></b><br />
LORE ITEM NO DROP <br />
Slot: EAR<br />
AC: 5<br />
Effect: Circle of Combines (Must Equip. Casting Time:24.0)<br />
STR: +8 &nbsp;&nbsp;STA: +8 &nbsp;&nbsp;WIS: +10 &nbsp;&nbsp;HP: +55 &nbsp;&nbsp;MANA: +55 &nbsp;&nbsp;<br />
SV FIRE: +7 &nbsp;&nbsp;SV COLD: +7 &nbsp;&nbsp;SV MAGIC: +7 &nbsp;&nbsp;<br />
WT: 0.1 &nbsp;&nbsp;Size: TINY<br />
Class: DRU <br />
Race: ALL<br />
Slot type 7:empty<br />

</p>
<p>
and
</p>
<p>
<b><a href="/items/show_item.php?item=1793&menustr=">spell: protection of the cabbage</a></b><br />
NO DROP <br />
Charges: 1<br />
Level Needed: 59<br />
Mana Cost: 500<br />
WT: 0.1 &nbsp;&nbsp;Size: SMALL<br />
Class: DRU <br />
Race: ALL<br />

</p>
<p>
<i>**Should the above earring not be to your taste (or you're not a druid), you can hand Xanthe's Earring of Nature to Rebecca Cabbageleaf in Fungus Grove. She will give you the following in return:</i>
</p>
<p>
<b><a href="/items/show_item.php?item=1770&menustr=">earring of the solstice</a></b><br />
LORE ITEM NO DROP <br />
Slot: EAR<br />
AC: 5<br />
STA: +5 &nbsp;&nbsp;WIS: +8 &nbsp;&nbsp;INT: +8 &nbsp;&nbsp;HP: +55 &nbsp;&nbsp;MANA: +55 &nbsp;&nbsp;<br />
SV FIRE: +5 &nbsp;&nbsp;SV COLD: +5 &nbsp;&nbsp;SV MAGIC: +5 &nbsp;&nbsp;<br />
Mana regeneration: +1<br />Recommended level of 51<br />
WT: 0.1 &nbsp;&nbsp;Size: TINY<br />
Class: ALL<br />
Race: ALL<br />
Slot type 7:empty<br />

</p>
